Implements the Tasks.md additions:

- #3 Weekly time tracker (metcon/strength/total) via weekTimeByCategory;
  surfaced in the weekly summary table.
- #4 Strength sessions fixed at 60 min (sessionTiming lift branch).
- #5 Long-run progression: redistribution-only enforceLongRun ramps the
  long run toward the 90-min cap and >=1.5x the easy runs (mileage-exact,
  golden HYROX untouched).
- #6 Actual Miles / Actual Cardio Time columns from workout logs.
- #7 Daily resting HR + HRV: migration 0026 (daily_metrics), schema,
  query, POST /api/daily-metrics, DailyMetricsForm, weekly averages
  (weeklyRecoveryAverages) shown as Recovery avg columns.
- #8 Swim + bike training zones always shown (%FTP / effort fallbacks).
- #9 Bike workouts FTP-based with secondary HR (%LTHR) cue; swim CSS-paced.
- #10 Weekly summary table moved full-width; no horizontal scroll.
- #11 Cycling long ride capped at 75% of race bike distance (phase-gated,
  2.5-3.5h base/build, up to ~5h peak for 140.6) + short easy brick run.
- #1/#2 Apple App Store + Stripe plans under docs/plans/.

Gates: tsc clean, vitest 446 passing (golden HYROX green), next build OK.
Migration 0026 is NOT applied — Levi applies it in Supabase.

